name: God Phoenix Gearfried
desc: Banish 1 Equip Spell you control or in your GY; Special Summon this card from your hand. When this card attacks, during the start of damage calculation: You can equip 1 face-up monster on the field to this card as an Equip. The equipped monster gains 500 ATK. (max. 1). When a monster activates its effect (Quick Effect): You can send 1 face-up Equip you control to the GY; negate that activation, and if you do, destroy that card. You can only use each effect of "God Phoenix Gearfried" once per turn.
